rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0001
rows.name:
There's a look about you...
the look of someone who buys
a lot of things at shops!

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm an up-and-coming economist,
and I'm trying to encourage people
to up their consumer activity.

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Whether buying or selling, what matters
is that money changes hands. That's
what keeps the economy flowing!

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0004
rows.name:
And if the economy thrives,
so will this city!

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0005
rows.name:
What's that mean for you,
I hear you ask?

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Well, it means you'll be able to
buy things cheaper!
